// ============================================================
// Test: like_disguise.ncs
// Purpose: Test Like command - disguise pool content as another command.
//   - Open a file, capture content
//   - Use Like to disguise the content as another command
//   - Verify the disguised command is in exec_cmds
// ============================================================

// -- Step 1: Open the docs file and capture --
!@Open ./tests/data/docs_guide.md
@/Open | Capture doc_pool

// -- Step 2: Disguise the captured content as an Open command --
!@Like doc_pool like=Open

// -- Step 3: Now pretend to be in an Open context; use another Open --
!@Open ./tests/data/docs_guide.md
!@Location
## Troubleshooting
!@New
### Performance Issues

If you see high CPU usage, check the worker thread count.
@/Location
@/Open
